WEBVTT

00:12.510 --> 00:17.690
[2009]

00:17.190 --> 00:17.870
Chuan,

00:20.420 --> 00:22.480
I want to discuss something with you.

00:25.070 --> 00:26.800
Where did you get this pocket watch

00:26.800 --> 00:27.800
and police badge?

00:28.280 --> 00:29.560
Is it issued by the SWAT team?

00:29.560 --> 00:31.740
It's a souvenir
from the provincial sniper competition.

00:31.740 --> 00:32.750
A souvenir?

00:33.350 --> 00:34.480
You got eliminated?

00:34.680 --> 00:36.280
Only the first place gets it.

00:36.970 --> 00:38.100
You got first place?

00:39.850 --> 00:41.520
First place only gets a souvenir?

00:41.520 --> 00:42.800
That's so stingy.

00:43.390 --> 00:44.650
You don't understand.

00:45.480 --> 00:47.010
Why wouldn't I understand?

00:47.760 --> 00:49.160
My birthday is coming up.

00:49.490 --> 00:50.750
Don't you understand?

00:50.750 --> 00:52.450
I'm cleaning it for you right now.

00:52.450 --> 00:53.510
Are you satisfied?

00:53.560 --> 00:55.620
I'm very satisfied. You know me best.

00:56.240 --> 00:56.750
You loot

00:57.250 --> 00:59.250
all my good stuff.

01:00.350 --> 01:01.850
What did you want to tell me?

01:01.850 --> 01:02.490
Yes.

01:06.610 --> 01:07.050
Chuan,

01:07.730 --> 01:09.130
I want to change my major.

01:09.700 --> 01:10.880
I think criminal investigation

01:10.880 --> 01:11.810
suits me better.

01:12.380 --> 01:13.180
Is Jiang Cheng

01:13.200 --> 01:14.280
really that good?

01:14.680 --> 01:16.080
I want to change my major.

01:16.690 --> 01:18.590
What does it have to do with Jiang Cheng?

01:18.590 --> 01:19.920
You applied to Jingzhou Police Academy

01:19.920 --> 01:20.950
just because of him.

01:20.950 --> 01:22.680
Jiang Cheng is a
criminal police officer now.

01:22.680 --> 01:23.700
And you can't hold back anymore.

01:23.700 --> 01:25.210
How is it because of him?

01:26.100 --> 01:27.770
Why can't it be because of you?

01:28.610 --> 01:30.210
Can't you be more confident?

01:30.640 --> 01:31.410
Besides,

01:31.700 --> 01:33.860
I've loved watching
Armed Reaction since I was a kid.

01:33.860 --> 01:35.060
That female cop

01:35.710 --> 01:36.479
is so cool!

01:38.550 --> 01:39.710
Being a female criminal cop

01:39.710 --> 01:41.120
is so hard, sister.

01:41.509 --> 01:42.150
Chuan,

01:42.509 --> 01:44.570
Mom and Dad already don't support me.

01:45.509 --> 01:47.240
If you don't support me either,

01:47.539 --> 01:50.210
I will be completely left alone.

01:50.240 --> 01:51.530
I'm so lonely.

01:51.550 --> 01:52.810
Do you know what facing loneliness

01:52.810 --> 01:54.090
means at my age?

01:54.340 --> 01:56.060
Loneliness is cruel.

01:56.289 --> 01:57.820
I need your support, Chuan.

01:57.990 --> 01:58.810
If I don't have you,

01:58.810 --> 02:00.620
I feel my life is hopeless.

02:00.640 --> 02:02.030
Alright, Jin.

02:02.790 --> 02:03.990
No matter what you do,

02:04.200 --> 02:05.260
I will support you,

02:05.400 --> 02:05.920
okay?

02:10.770 --> 02:11.330
Really?

02:11.710 --> 02:12.240
Yes.

02:12.590 --> 02:13.710
With me behind you,

02:14.200 --> 02:15.060
you can just...

02:16.540 --> 02:17.840
I can just...

02:19.500 --> 02:23.780
♪ Sister, be brave and walk forward ♪

02:24.340 --> 02:25.260
Don't look back!

02:25.260 --> 02:27.610
♪ Don't look back ♪

03:52.770 --> 03:58.310
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:58.670 --> 04:01.130
[Episode 9]

04:04.090 --> 04:05.550
Let's just have some beer.

04:05.810 --> 04:07.000
Let's play a game.

04:07.930 --> 04:08.740
What game?

04:09.190 --> 04:10.590
Let me ask you a question.

04:11.360 --> 04:12.540
If you don't want to answer,

04:12.540 --> 04:13.380
you take a sip.

04:17.720 --> 04:18.370
Zhou Jin,

04:19.339 --> 04:20.660
are you mad at me?

04:20.730 --> 04:21.560
Cut the crap.

04:21.839 --> 04:23.100
Are you playing or not?

04:24.340 --> 04:24.900
Okay.

04:25.490 --> 04:26.130
Ask away.

04:29.930 --> 04:32.390
When did you
become a university professor?

04:37.420 --> 04:38.350
Three years ago.

04:39.440 --> 04:41.130
And when did you leave
the Provincial Bureau?

04:41.130 --> 04:42.130
About 5 years ago.

04:43.540 --> 04:45.460
Pretty convenient timing—

04:45.680 --> 04:47.280
showing up on our team
as a special consultant.

04:47.280 --> 04:48.810
That's not so simple, is it?

04:52.250 --> 04:52.900
Zhou Jin,

04:54.490 --> 04:55.690
I am not your suspect.

04:57.420 --> 04:59.540
Starting with trivial,
irrelevant questions,

04:59.540 --> 05:00.470
using gestures

05:00.560 --> 05:02.050
to subtly stimulate responses,

05:02.050 --> 05:03.220
then building an association

05:03.220 --> 05:05.300
between those gestures
and telling the truth—

05:05.300 --> 05:07.490
that's one of the techniques
used in interrogation.

05:07.490 --> 05:08.950
Pavlovian conditioning.

05:09.900 --> 05:12.160
It's the first lesson in interrogation.

05:12.610 --> 05:13.250
Zhou Jin,

05:14.170 --> 05:15.230
don't do this to me.

05:24.900 --> 05:25.570
Sorry.

05:27.570 --> 05:28.900
Whatever you want to ask,

05:28.900 --> 05:29.900
I will answer you.

05:33.130 --> 05:33.780
Okay.

05:34.370 --> 05:35.970
Then I'll just ask directly.

05:36.610 --> 05:37.540
Do you like me?

05:38.490 --> 05:39.170
Yes, I do.

05:39.980 --> 05:41.570
Since when?

05:42.980 --> 05:44.180
Since our blind date.

05:44.670 --> 05:45.670
Why do you like me?

05:47.170 --> 05:48.430
With your conditions,

05:49.170 --> 05:51.300
you could easily find someone better.

05:51.780 --> 05:52.710
Someone like me—

05:53.650 --> 05:55.909
always busy with work, hardly ever home.

05:56.370 --> 05:58.050
You could've chosen someone

05:58.540 --> 05:59.659
gentler,

05:59.659 --> 06:00.570
prettier,

06:00.690 --> 06:02.050
and who could take better care of you.

06:02.050 --> 06:03.780
There's no one better than you.

06:16.780 --> 06:17.780
Did you marry me

06:18.610 --> 06:20.010
because you love me,

06:21.120 --> 06:22.850
or was there some other reason?

06:25.300 --> 06:28.300
You've been involved in
the investigation all along.

06:28.460 --> 06:30.420
You already knew everything

06:30.780 --> 06:32.460
without me telling you about my brother,

06:32.460 --> 06:33.010
right?

06:35.780 --> 06:36.780
Who told you that?

06:37.100 --> 06:38.760
It doesn't matter who said it.

06:39.780 --> 06:41.810
I'm right, aren't I?

06:54.280 --> 06:57.810
5 years ago, the last time
you came into contact with that group,

06:58.180 --> 07:00.110
it was because of the lead you gave,

07:00.340 --> 07:01.100
wasn't it?

07:01.660 --> 07:02.300
Zhou Jin,

07:02.570 --> 07:03.420
it's unfair.

07:03.810 --> 07:05.170
This is the same question.

07:05.170 --> 07:07.010
You don't have to answer my question.

07:07.010 --> 07:08.140
Then keep drinking.

07:08.300 --> 07:09.300
But I have to ask.

07:42.250 --> 07:43.690
If it were anyone else,

07:44.150 --> 07:46.350
I would definitely try my best to ask him

07:46.610 --> 07:48.370
everything he knows.

07:49.860 --> 07:51.990
But when I found out that person is you,

07:53.690 --> 07:55.980
that was not the first thing I thought of.

07:56.680 --> 07:57.740
What I care about is

07:59.159 --> 07:59.870
exactly why

07:59.890 --> 08:01.620
you stayed by my side.

08:02.930 --> 08:04.100
Why have you

08:04.380 --> 08:06.060
never told me about this?

08:06.170 --> 08:07.770
What exactly are you hiding?

08:09.690 --> 08:10.370
Zhou Jin.

08:10.420 --> 08:11.350
Jiang Hansheng,

08:13.930 --> 08:15.490
please don't lie to me.

08:44.490 --> 08:45.820
You've heard of

08:46.650 --> 08:48.780
the Huaiguang serial murders, right?

08:49.960 --> 08:56.340
[1997]

08:55.410 --> 08:57.010
Back then in Huaiguang City,

08:57.580 --> 08:59.040
3 women were successively

08:59.490 --> 09:00.860
murdered in their own homes

09:00.860 --> 09:02.530
in just 3 short months,

09:04.060 --> 09:06.340
The most striking commonality
among the 3 cases

09:06.340 --> 09:07.610
was that the female victims

09:07.610 --> 09:09.670
were all wearing bright red dresses,

09:10.290 --> 09:12.620
lying on a bed scattered with rose petals.

09:14.220 --> 09:16.280
The fatal wound was a cut to the wrist.

09:16.860 --> 09:18.460
A bow was tied over the wound.

09:19.700 --> 09:20.940
Excessive blood loss

09:21.410 --> 09:22.610
caused their deaths.

09:23.010 --> 09:23.700
Prof was working

09:23.700 --> 09:25.700
at the Huaiguang CIB.

09:26.180 --> 09:27.820
Initially, his investigative approach

09:27.820 --> 09:29.750
focused heavily on the first case.

09:30.940 --> 09:32.170
He wanted to start from the beginning

09:32.170 --> 09:35.010
to quickly find the motive
behind the ritualistic killings.

09:35.010 --> 09:37.940
Despite deploying a large
police force for searches,

09:37.940 --> 09:38.580
checking

09:39.250 --> 09:40.710
all kinds of petty thieves

09:40.900 --> 09:42.960
and suspects with criminal records,

09:43.820 --> 09:45.620
there was no real breakthrough.

09:45.890 --> 09:47.740
Was there any narrowing
of the suspect pool?

09:47.740 --> 09:48.370
Hardly.

09:49.130 --> 09:50.250
The scene lacked

09:50.280 --> 09:51.760
traceable evidence,

09:52.530 --> 09:54.990
and no usable fingerprints were collected.

09:55.610 --> 09:58.820
This person's counter-surveillance skills
are really strong.

09:58.820 --> 09:59.370
Did you make

09:59.370 --> 10:01.030
a criminal profiling report?

10:01.370 --> 10:02.010
Of course.

10:02.890 --> 10:04.650
But criminal profiling at the time

10:04.650 --> 10:05.770
was not yet mature enough

10:05.770 --> 10:08.170
to be directly applied in investigations.

10:08.460 --> 10:10.390
It didn't receive much attention.

10:11.770 --> 10:13.700
Just when the police were at a loss,

10:14.890 --> 10:16.750
someone claiming to be the killer

10:17.100 --> 10:18.160
turned himself in.

10:18.490 --> 10:19.550
Turned himself in?

10:22.910 --> 10:24.080
He was an accountant

10:24.710 --> 10:25.590
named Chen Li.

10:27.990 --> 10:29.620
The Huaiguang serial murder cases

10:29.620 --> 10:31.380
were able to be closed back then

10:31.640 --> 10:33.570
because Chen Li turned himself in.

10:34.140 --> 10:36.880
The police took Chen Li
to identify the crime scenes.

10:36.880 --> 10:38.330
He described his crime process

10:38.330 --> 10:39.560
very clearly.

10:40.370 --> 10:42.760
The details of his confession

10:43.130 --> 10:45.190
matched the crime scenes perfectly.

10:45.640 --> 10:46.900
What about the motive?

10:48.010 --> 10:50.040
He said he was dissatisfied with
his ex-wife's cheating

10:50.040 --> 10:52.700
and committed serial murders
to vent his anger.

10:53.530 --> 10:55.960
The details of the crime
were never disclosed.

10:55.960 --> 10:57.230
Only the killer would know

10:57.230 --> 10:58.220
the details of the crime best.

10:58.220 --> 10:59.680
Then he must be the killer.

11:01.210 --> 11:02.810
There was only one loophole.

11:03.040 --> 11:04.370
In the first case,

11:04.830 --> 11:06.430
the forensic doctor found

11:06.450 --> 11:08.380
sperm stains on the victim's body.

11:08.480 --> 11:09.840
DNA testing proved that

11:10.640 --> 11:12.170
it didn't belong to Chen Li.

11:12.960 --> 11:14.890
That's a major point of suspicion.

11:16.600 --> 11:18.500
The explanation given at that time was

11:18.500 --> 11:20.060
that the victim had sex with other men

11:20.060 --> 11:21.650
before she was murdered.

11:23.760 --> 11:26.550
This suspect point wasn't
carefully investigated

11:26.550 --> 11:28.080
before the case was closed.

11:28.720 --> 11:30.090
That's too arbitrary.

11:31.530 --> 11:33.690
Your reaction is exactly
the same as Prof's.

11:33.690 --> 11:34.450
I heard

11:34.470 --> 11:36.600
he stormed into the captain's office,

11:36.840 --> 11:38.300
almost flipping the desk,

11:38.510 --> 11:39.960
insisting the case couldn't be closed.

11:39.960 --> 11:40.920
I can totally picture

11:40.920 --> 11:42.580
what Prof must have been like.

11:43.100 --> 11:44.320
But the person involved

11:44.320 --> 11:45.250
didn't admit it.

11:48.570 --> 11:50.430
But there was nothing we could do.

11:50.880 --> 11:52.940
Chen Li showed up at the perfect time.

11:54.650 --> 11:55.790
Then what did Prof think

11:55.790 --> 11:57.390
the killer should look like?

11:59.250 --> 12:00.580
A local from Huaiguang,

12:01.010 --> 12:03.210
a middle-aged single man living alone,

12:03.440 --> 12:04.570
without a steady job

12:05.010 --> 12:06.740
but with some financial means,

12:07.520 --> 12:08.850
or someone persuasive,

12:09.570 --> 12:10.770
or with decent looks.

12:11.800 --> 12:12.560
Leaders,

12:13.690 --> 12:15.810
the times of the 3 murders

12:15.840 --> 12:17.440
show no particular pattern.

12:17.800 --> 12:20.640
One happened during a holiday,

12:21.070 --> 12:23.790
and two on weekdays.

12:24.050 --> 12:25.210
What does this mean?

12:25.680 --> 12:27.380
It means the killer isn't bound

12:27.380 --> 12:29.380
by an employer's attendance rules.

12:29.610 --> 12:30.300
Of course,

12:30.560 --> 12:31.760
the killer might also

12:31.760 --> 12:32.640
be unemployed.

12:33.990 --> 12:35.770
From the moment he chose his target

12:35.770 --> 12:37.860
to the act of killing,

12:37.890 --> 12:39.130
there were no signs of

12:39.150 --> 12:41.080
resistance or struggle.

12:41.670 --> 12:43.380
The victims had no

12:43.590 --> 12:44.470
binding marks

12:44.560 --> 12:45.670
or defensive injuries.

12:45.670 --> 12:47.170
We've examined the scenes,

12:47.170 --> 12:49.230
and the doors and windows are intact.

12:49.340 --> 12:50.600
What does this tell us?

12:50.800 --> 12:51.540
It tells us

12:51.770 --> 12:53.730
the victims willingly

12:53.730 --> 12:55.340
brought the killer home.

12:55.650 --> 12:56.510
In other words,

12:56.860 --> 12:58.340
this man was very attractive

12:58.340 --> 12:59.770
in the eyes of women.

12:59.860 --> 13:01.520
So what makes him attractive?

13:01.700 --> 13:03.800
Nothing more than money, talent, or looks.

13:03.800 --> 13:04.350
Right?

13:04.890 --> 13:07.250
Chen Li is a petty accountant
at a small company,

13:07.250 --> 13:08.910
earning peanuts every month.

13:09.650 --> 13:11.940
He's plain-looking
and can't even speak clearly.

13:11.940 --> 13:13.250
He's unpopular at work,

13:13.250 --> 13:14.730
and his family is average.

13:14.730 --> 13:15.980
Chen Li

13:16.490 --> 13:19.410
fits none of the suspect's profiles.

13:19.610 --> 13:22.300
How could he be the killer?

13:23.100 --> 13:24.130
Impossible.

13:26.430 --> 13:28.070
In the Huaiguang series of cases,

13:28.070 --> 13:29.490
the most distinct feature

13:29.490 --> 13:31.250
is that when choosing targets,

13:31.580 --> 13:33.580
the killer has a specific tendency.

13:36.300 --> 13:37.730
Women in red dresses?

13:39.650 --> 13:40.650
That's crucial.

13:41.410 --> 13:43.100
It's an important criterion

13:43.150 --> 13:44.580
the killer uses
when selecting his targets,

13:44.580 --> 13:46.010
and it's the underlying motive

13:46.010 --> 13:47.530
running through
the entire serial murder cases.

13:47.530 --> 13:49.290
There was a woman in a red dress

13:49.700 --> 13:51.360
whom the killer hated deeply.

13:51.580 --> 13:52.410
He killed women

13:52.410 --> 13:53.820
who resembled her

13:53.840 --> 13:54.840
to vent his anger.

13:54.880 --> 13:55.960
Was it his wife?

14:01.490 --> 14:03.130
From what I know,

14:03.160 --> 14:04.350
that's about it.

14:05.250 --> 14:06.490
I don't really know

14:06.890 --> 14:08.200
anything else.

14:11.980 --> 14:13.580
Can I see your closet?

14:13.890 --> 14:14.460
Sure.

14:15.060 --> 14:15.610
This way.

14:22.220 --> 14:23.940
All my clothes are here.

14:30.100 --> 14:31.430
Do you wear red dresses?

14:33.270 --> 14:35.030
I never wear red clothes.

14:36.370 --> 14:38.300
Prof went to see Chen Li's ex-wife.

14:38.520 --> 14:41.320
She turned out to be
a traditional and plain woman.

14:41.530 --> 14:42.460
Her style of dress

14:42.460 --> 14:43.920
was almost conservative.

14:44.530 --> 14:46.250
She said she had never worn a red dress,

14:46.250 --> 14:47.650
let alone cheated on him.

14:48.010 --> 14:48.940
They divorced

14:48.940 --> 14:49.610
simply because

14:49.610 --> 14:51.810
of their incompatible personalities.

14:52.180 --> 14:54.530
Doesn't that prove he was lying?

14:54.940 --> 14:56.770
Couldn't the case be overturned?

14:56.770 --> 14:59.100
Prof didn't have time to submit the report

14:59.800 --> 15:00.930
before Chen Li died.

15:02.290 --> 15:03.520
He died of liver cancer

15:03.520 --> 15:04.590
in custody.

15:07.530 --> 15:08.730
Then I have an answer.

15:11.410 --> 15:12.250
It's a guess,

15:12.860 --> 15:13.660
not an answer.

15:14.650 --> 15:15.980
We all have our guesses.

15:16.720 --> 15:19.180
Chen Li might have taken the fall
for someone else.

15:19.180 --> 15:20.060
The killer

15:20.330 --> 15:22.060
could have told him all the details

15:22.060 --> 15:23.660
and made him turn himself in.

15:24.980 --> 15:26.380
Until there's evidence,

15:26.940 --> 15:29.270
speculation is always just speculation.

15:29.940 --> 15:31.000
After Chen Li died,

15:31.340 --> 15:32.410
there really haven't been

15:32.410 --> 15:33.610
any similar murders.

15:34.590 --> 15:35.920
And criminal profiling

15:36.180 --> 15:38.410
has always remained
at the theoretical stage.

15:38.410 --> 15:39.140
It has always

15:39.730 --> 15:42.390
only served as
a reference for investigations.

15:44.010 --> 15:45.200
Sometimes the truth will prove

15:45.200 --> 15:47.260
that the theory is completely wrong.

15:54.370 --> 15:55.180
Are you okay?

15:55.410 --> 15:56.210
What's wrong?

15:57.060 --> 15:57.650
I'm fine.

15:59.220 --> 16:01.550
But you haven't answered my question yet.

16:01.820 --> 16:03.080
What's the connection

16:03.100 --> 16:04.770
between the Huaiguang serial cases,

16:04.770 --> 16:06.430
the 8/17 Case, and my brother?

16:07.610 --> 16:09.010
Regarding the 8/17 Case,

16:09.080 --> 16:11.580
you only know about
your brother Zhou Chuan's sacrifice

16:11.580 --> 16:13.700
and that his service gun
went missing, right?

16:13.700 --> 16:14.580
I also know

16:15.580 --> 16:16.490
that the gang of criminals

16:16.490 --> 16:17.890
was caught by Leader Yao,

16:18.060 --> 16:19.590
and you were the informant.

16:21.460 --> 16:22.660
What you don't know is

16:23.100 --> 16:24.700
that before your brother died,

16:24.700 --> 16:26.060
he had a close-quarters fight

16:26.060 --> 16:27.700
with the 8/17 Case criminals.

16:27.700 --> 16:29.300
The police extracted bloodstains

16:29.300 --> 16:30.560
from his fingernails.

16:31.190 --> 16:32.630
The DNA of the bloodstains

16:32.630 --> 16:33.530
matched the DNA from the sperm stains

16:33.530 --> 16:35.340
in the Huaiguang Case

16:35.530 --> 16:36.530
from 20 years ago.

16:38.740 --> 16:39.590
Are they...

16:40.610 --> 16:42.010
Are they the same person?

16:42.130 --> 16:43.730
Because of this connection,

16:44.100 --> 16:44.650
and with the 8/17 Case

16:44.650 --> 16:46.580
making no progress for a long time,

16:46.650 --> 16:48.340
the Provincial Bureau decided

16:48.340 --> 16:50.130
to start with the Huaiguang Case

16:50.130 --> 16:52.460
to find this participant
in the 8/17 Case.

16:53.610 --> 16:55.610
But the Huaiguang Case
is also full of doubts,

16:55.610 --> 16:57.180
and they couldn't catch anyone at all.

16:57.180 --> 16:58.580
We start from the doubts.

16:58.940 --> 17:00.490
Based on the profile back then,

17:00.490 --> 17:01.980
Prof screened a lot of people.

17:01.980 --> 17:04.130
These people were all cleared of suspicion

17:04.130 --> 17:05.930
during further investigation.

17:07.740 --> 17:09.000
Was the profile wrong?

17:10.210 --> 17:11.099
You are right.

17:12.650 --> 17:14.450
After reopening the Huaiguang Case,

17:14.450 --> 17:16.300
Prof gave me all the evidence records

17:16.300 --> 17:17.780
collected by the police back then

17:17.780 --> 17:19.910
and asked me to issue a profile report.

17:20.369 --> 17:22.170
He was afraid his thoughts
would influence me,

17:22.170 --> 17:23.099
so he didn't tell me

17:23.099 --> 17:25.410
he had already written
a profile back then.

17:25.410 --> 17:27.609
Was there any difference in the result?

17:30.820 --> 17:31.370
Age.

17:32.650 --> 17:35.180
I don't think the killer
is a middle-aged man,

17:35.650 --> 17:36.650
but a young person

17:36.970 --> 17:39.130
between the ages of 18 and 23.

17:40.130 --> 17:41.990
The crime scenes, full of ritual,

17:42.270 --> 17:43.060
easily masked the original motive

17:43.060 --> 17:44.650
for the killings.

17:47.970 --> 17:48.540
Zhou Jin,

17:49.430 --> 17:50.630
are you looking at me?

17:53.540 --> 17:54.130
No.

17:54.890 --> 17:56.020
You are lying again.

18:07.650 --> 18:08.450
What's wrong?

18:08.890 --> 18:10.930
You got drunk on a bottle of cola?

18:11.890 --> 18:12.750
It wasn't cola,

18:13.170 --> 18:13.900
but seafood.

18:14.980 --> 18:16.380
I'm allergic to seafood.

18:17.860 --> 18:19.260
You're allergic to

18:19.690 --> 18:21.370
seafood-flavored instant noodles?

18:21.370 --> 18:22.170
Come on.

18:22.500 --> 18:22.970
I am.

18:23.410 --> 18:25.470
I just didn't get a chance to tell you.

18:30.540 --> 18:31.600
Do you have a fever?

18:33.650 --> 18:34.260
I'm fine.

18:35.210 --> 18:36.540
I'll be fine in a minute.

18:47.290 --> 18:47.940
Let's go.

18:51.210 --> 18:52.410
If you need anything,

18:52.410 --> 18:53.340
you must tell me.

18:58.890 --> 18:59.490
By the way,

19:00.020 --> 19:01.020
where were we?

19:02.780 --> 19:04.040
Criminal motivation.

19:04.610 --> 19:06.060
So you mean,

19:06.890 --> 19:08.060
no matter how fancy

19:08.060 --> 19:09.820
the killer arranged the scene,

19:10.130 --> 19:11.410
his original motivation

19:11.410 --> 19:12.870
was still sexual assault.

19:14.450 --> 19:16.260
A sex-driven crime.

19:18.930 --> 19:19.940
Since the killer

19:19.960 --> 19:22.410
could make the victim
take him home back then,

19:22.410 --> 19:23.260
it shows he had

19:23.260 --> 19:24.920
the ability to attract women.

19:26.100 --> 19:27.300
Logically speaking,

19:27.300 --> 19:28.370
he didn't lack women.

19:28.370 --> 19:29.390
There were 2 situations where

19:29.390 --> 19:31.390
he couldn't be satisfied sexually.

19:31.740 --> 19:32.430
First,

19:32.780 --> 19:34.310
he has sexual dysfunction.

19:34.860 --> 19:35.690
Second,

19:36.370 --> 19:38.210
the way he interacts with women

19:38.210 --> 19:40.270
was quite different from normal men.

19:41.240 --> 19:43.170
But the first has been ruled out.

19:43.500 --> 19:45.130
Because semen was extracted

19:45.260 --> 19:47.120
from the female corpse back then.

19:47.260 --> 19:48.370
So I think

19:48.860 --> 19:50.450
it should be the latter.

19:51.500 --> 19:52.460
The women took him home

19:52.460 --> 19:54.100
not necessarily because of his charm,

19:54.100 --> 19:55.340
but possibly because he triggered

19:55.340 --> 19:56.940
their protective instinct.

19:57.610 --> 19:59.180
Middle-aged men easily make women

19:59.180 --> 20:00.490
naturally defensive.

20:00.670 --> 20:02.890
But young men have an advantage
in this regard.

20:02.890 --> 20:03.650
Are you okay?

20:04.520 --> 20:05.650
We're almost there.

20:06.170 --> 20:07.610
Based on the trace inspection report,

20:07.610 --> 20:09.340
I conclude that he is a petite,

20:09.340 --> 20:10.300
and frail,

20:10.410 --> 20:12.860
young man who doesn't look very strong.

20:14.300 --> 20:15.300
When he appeared,

20:15.340 --> 20:17.000
he was extremely vulnerable.

20:18.740 --> 20:20.590
Among the 3 murder cases,

20:21.410 --> 20:24.010
the victims' ages
are showing an upward trend.

20:24.410 --> 20:25.690
This indicates that the killer

20:25.690 --> 20:27.970
prefers to choose more mature women.

20:28.890 --> 20:30.020
So I infer

20:30.460 --> 20:32.650
that the killer may not
have lacked romantic relationships,

20:32.650 --> 20:34.610
but rather had a problematic relationship
with his mother in his early years.

20:34.610 --> 20:36.090
He is from a single-parent family,

20:36.090 --> 20:37.690
raised solely by his mother,

20:37.860 --> 20:40.410
and has very serious
psychological problems.

20:40.410 --> 20:41.300
And it is very likely

20:41.300 --> 20:42.690
that he suffered betrayal,

20:42.690 --> 20:44.770
abandonment, and torture from his mother,

20:44.770 --> 20:46.540
leading to a twisted personality.

20:46.540 --> 20:48.070
While obsessed with women,

20:48.140 --> 20:49.600
he also deeply hates them.

21:00.860 --> 21:01.450
But

21:01.820 --> 21:04.080
15 years have passed since the incident.

21:04.690 --> 21:06.020
Even with a new profile,

21:06.820 --> 21:08.540
we couldn't catch the criminal

21:08.540 --> 21:09.780
in such a short time.

21:11.210 --> 21:12.410
But you have clues.

21:15.170 --> 21:16.970
The real murderer is not Chen Li,

21:17.300 --> 21:18.020
but Qi Yan.

21:19.540 --> 21:20.300
Qi Yan,

21:21.740 --> 21:24.000
the one who stabbed Cheng over ten times?

21:30.770 --> 21:31.960
How did you know him?

21:35.170 --> 21:37.410
Knowing the criminal's
personality weaknesses

21:37.410 --> 21:39.210
means knowing how to enrage him.

21:40.580 --> 21:41.860
I just threw out bait,

21:42.500 --> 21:43.300
and he took it.

21:43.650 --> 21:44.410
What bait?

21:47.740 --> 21:48.100
Me.

21:52.820 --> 21:54.020
He showed up in person

21:54.410 --> 21:55.540
to invite me over.

21:57.500 --> 21:58.170
And then?

21:59.260 --> 21:59.860
Then,

22:01.500 --> 22:02.500
he was arrested.

22:03.540 --> 22:04.600
It was a close call.

22:05.840 --> 22:06.780
Leader Yao and I

22:06.860 --> 22:08.260
had prepared in advance.

22:08.780 --> 22:10.110
He arrived just in time.

22:12.340 --> 22:13.860
You make it sound so easy.

22:16.450 --> 22:17.450
It was at that time

22:18.450 --> 22:19.650
Leader Yao led his men

22:20.170 --> 22:21.700
to take down their hideout.

22:23.210 --> 22:24.410
But looking at it now,

22:24.540 --> 22:25.270
it's obvious

22:26.060 --> 22:28.120
that he had a sizable gang behind him.

22:28.450 --> 22:29.310
Where's Qi Yan?

22:31.220 --> 22:31.850
He's dead.

22:34.260 --> 22:35.260
I guessed as much.

22:36.890 --> 22:38.540
At that time, as family members,

22:38.540 --> 22:39.690
they told us

22:40.380 --> 22:42.300
there were at least 2 attackers.

22:43.100 --> 22:44.630
One was brought to justice,

22:44.930 --> 22:45.660
and the other

22:46.450 --> 22:48.130
ran away with the gun.

22:49.370 --> 22:51.540
Then they told us this case

22:52.130 --> 22:54.130
would continue to be investigated.

22:55.060 --> 22:55.990
It has continued

22:56.060 --> 22:57.610
up to this day.

23:03.410 --> 23:04.120
Zhou Jin,

23:09.130 --> 23:10.330
we didn't find the gun

23:11.410 --> 23:12.500
or find out

23:13.060 --> 23:14.320
why your brother died.

23:15.880 --> 23:16.770
I'm sorry.

23:22.740 --> 23:24.470
What do you have to be sorry for?

23:25.970 --> 23:27.050
I actually didn't leave

23:27.050 --> 23:28.910
the CID of the Provincial Bureau.

23:29.060 --> 23:31.190
My identity as a university professor

23:31.210 --> 23:33.210
was just to hide my identity as a cop.

23:34.940 --> 23:36.020
I won't give up.

23:39.060 --> 23:39.780
So,

23:40.530 --> 23:42.060
you've been a cop all along.

23:49.410 --> 23:50.100
Thank you,

23:50.820 --> 23:51.750
Jiang Hansheng.

24:04.450 --> 24:05.740
Tell me more about it.

24:06.500 --> 24:07.300
At that time,

24:08.020 --> 24:09.350
how did you piss him off?

24:09.840 --> 24:11.170
What method did you use?

24:14.500 --> 24:15.900
I don't seem to remember.

24:17.170 --> 24:17.890
Then,

24:20.710 --> 24:22.770
what was his attitude when he saw you?

24:29.960 --> 24:31.420
Did he say anything to you?

24:32.100 --> 24:32.970
You were already

24:32.970 --> 24:34.370
in a life-or-death situation,

24:34.370 --> 24:35.970
he must have said something.

24:38.470 --> 24:39.870
I don't remember either.

24:40.780 --> 24:42.640
Why don't you remember anything?

24:43.300 --> 24:44.300
Then what do you

24:51.540 --> 24:52.450
remember?

25:02.650 --> 25:03.780
I remember Zhou Jin.

25:36.110 --> 25:37.770
The person who died 5 years ago

25:38.500 --> 25:39.340
was Mr. Yan.

25:40.380 --> 25:41.060
Mr. Yan?

25:42.370 --> 25:43.500
A respectful title.

25:44.130 --> 25:45.170
He was young,

25:45.300 --> 25:46.700
but highly influential.

25:47.740 --> 25:48.930
After he died,

25:49.820 --> 25:51.880
Old Scorpion laid low for a long time.

25:52.170 --> 25:53.130
Some say

25:53.970 --> 25:55.900
it was because he was traumatized.

25:55.930 --> 25:58.290
Others say it was because
he was short-handed

25:58.290 --> 25:59.690
and lost his confidence.

26:00.210 --> 26:01.740
You don't think so, Boss He?

26:03.930 --> 26:06.260
The 8/17 Case caused too much of a stir.

26:06.860 --> 26:08.210
Even Old Scorpion

26:08.820 --> 26:10.480
would have his reservations.

26:11.060 --> 26:11.580
Boss He,

26:12.130 --> 26:13.610
how did that Mr. Yan die?

26:13.920 --> 26:15.450
He was killed by the police.

26:15.740 --> 26:17.500
That's why Old Scorpion never let anyone

26:17.500 --> 26:19.130
touch the gun from 8/17 Case.

26:19.820 --> 26:20.780
Because Mr. Yan

26:22.010 --> 26:23.120
died that time.

26:25.100 --> 26:27.450
But Zhengtian just had to
steal it and use it.

26:27.450 --> 26:28.980
Isn't that courting death?

26:30.100 --> 26:30.610
Boss He,

26:31.290 --> 26:32.290
have you seen him?

26:34.820 --> 26:36.100
Do you mean Mr. Yan

26:36.520 --> 26:37.520
or Old Scorpion?

26:37.720 --> 26:39.520
You must have seen Old Scorpion.

26:41.410 --> 26:42.610
It's been years.

26:43.690 --> 26:45.020
After that case,

26:45.970 --> 26:47.630
Old Scorpion hid himself well

26:47.690 --> 26:49.150
and never showed up again.

26:52.020 --> 26:52.930
Then,

26:53.100 --> 26:54.160
what about  Mr. Yan?

26:55.060 --> 26:56.460
I only heard his stories,

26:57.160 --> 26:58.370
but never saw him.

27:02.380 --> 27:03.430
So mysterious.

27:05.690 --> 27:06.300
Boss He,

27:09.540 --> 27:10.740
everything is ready.

27:10.780 --> 27:11.300
Okay.

27:15.040 --> 27:15.610
Boss He.

27:15.860 --> 27:16.260
Come.

27:17.100 --> 27:17.930
Sit.

27:21.410 --> 27:22.690
Why aren't you eating?

27:24.280 --> 27:26.110
We have to put on a full show.

27:26.340 --> 27:27.600
We're coming out here camping.

27:27.600 --> 27:28.690
If your mood's off,

27:28.720 --> 27:29.850
it'll give you away.

27:30.180 --> 27:31.070
Come,

27:31.090 --> 27:31.690
have a drink.

27:31.690 --> 27:32.260
Come, Boss He.

27:32.260 --> 27:32.820
Come.

27:32.910 --> 27:33.440
Come.

27:36.450 --> 27:37.710
You guys eat and drink.

27:37.840 --> 27:39.770
Cheng, let's get down to business.

27:39.850 --> 27:40.330
Okay.

27:41.620 --> 27:42.270
Dahua.

27:45.060 --> 27:45.660
Everyone,

27:46.040 --> 27:47.640
hand over your phones first.

27:50.190 --> 27:51.840
No matter how many phones you brought,

27:51.840 --> 27:53.170
put them all in this box.

28:08.060 --> 28:09.170
From today on,

28:09.200 --> 28:10.450
everyone here is

28:10.450 --> 28:12.450
the backbone of Hengyun Logistics.

28:12.890 --> 28:14.890
This was personally appointed by Boss He

28:14.890 --> 28:16.450
after careful discussion
between him and me.

28:16.450 --> 28:18.130
After the power outage at the warehouse
a few days ago,

28:18.130 --> 28:19.210
I believe you all

28:19.240 --> 28:21.170
have heard something more or less.

28:21.820 --> 28:22.450
Indeed,

28:23.170 --> 28:25.170
there was a problem with that route.

28:25.650 --> 28:26.860
The reason why I brought you all

28:26.860 --> 28:27.890
to a place like this today

28:27.890 --> 28:29.130
is to tell you

28:29.410 --> 28:31.410
that we can't be so passive anymore.

28:32.130 --> 28:33.740
Boss He and I need your help

28:34.060 --> 28:35.460
to rebuild the new route.

28:35.610 --> 28:36.650
It must be fast

28:37.680 --> 28:38.480
and stable.

28:41.550 --> 28:42.680
This is what I think.

28:43.290 --> 28:45.570
We need to learn from Lai San's case.

28:45.970 --> 28:46.890
From now on,

28:47.060 --> 28:48.930
we will establish strict
organizational rules

28:48.930 --> 28:50.100
and structure.

28:50.540 --> 28:52.890
We will divide the personnel
into 4 levels.

28:52.890 --> 28:53.820
The top level is

28:54.050 --> 28:55.310
the regional manager—

28:55.650 --> 28:56.260
me.

29:01.690 --> 29:03.260
The regional manager
manages 6 store managers,

29:03.260 --> 29:04.930
which are the six of you.

29:05.690 --> 29:08.290
Each store manager
oversees a deputy manager.

29:08.860 --> 29:10.410
You guys decide

29:10.650 --> 29:12.920
the number of
frontline workers yourselves.

29:12.920 --> 29:13.730
Wait,

29:14.130 --> 29:15.590
this is a major reshuffle.

29:20.130 --> 29:21.060
Store managers?

29:21.370 --> 29:23.570
Why don't you just run a pyramid scheme?

29:27.130 --> 29:27.590
Yes,

29:28.060 --> 29:29.120
a major reshuffle.

29:29.220 --> 29:31.150
And we need to strengthen control.

29:31.880 --> 29:33.770
What if someone refuses to obey?

29:34.130 --> 29:36.170
The bottom-level staff can report
their superiors if they refuse to obey.

29:36.170 --> 29:37.780
I have the right
to dismiss store managers,

29:37.780 --> 29:38.930
but I don't have the power of appointment.

29:38.930 --> 29:41.060
The power of appointment
now belongs to Boss He.

29:41.060 --> 29:41.660
Of course,

29:42.020 --> 29:43.480
it will belong to everyone in the future.

29:43.480 --> 29:45.340
We respect the will of the people.

29:45.970 --> 29:48.690
If all 6 of you agree unanimously,

29:49.310 --> 29:50.180
you can also

29:50.210 --> 29:52.210
dismiss me as the regional manager.

29:54.970 --> 29:56.300
Are there any problems?

29:59.540 --> 30:01.400
Next, let's talk about the route.

30:01.890 --> 30:02.580
Xiao Mao!

30:03.260 --> 30:05.100
Cheng, the skewers will be ready soon.

30:05.100 --> 30:06.230
Bring us the phones.

30:14.510 --> 30:15.100
Boss He.

30:22.210 --> 30:23.500
Boss He's and my numbers are already

30:23.500 --> 30:24.860
saved on your phones.

30:25.130 --> 30:27.920
For the staff and routes
you're relatively familiar with,

30:27.920 --> 30:30.230
send them to me point-to-point
through this phone.

30:30.230 --> 30:31.970
I will consider them comprehensively.

30:31.970 --> 30:32.890
From now on,

30:33.130 --> 30:34.860
as long as it's about smuggling,

30:34.860 --> 30:37.120
we only communicate through this phone.

30:44.740 --> 30:45.340
Okay.

30:45.740 --> 30:47.000
Then I'll leave first.

30:47.500 --> 30:48.650
If you don't understand anything,

30:48.650 --> 30:49.690
you can ask Cheng.

30:53.650 --> 30:54.910
I didn't misjudge you.

30:55.060 --> 30:56.120
Thank you, Boss He.

30:57.820 --> 30:58.890
Take care, Boss He.

31:05.370 --> 31:07.370
Tonight we need to clarify a principle.

31:07.370 --> 31:09.500
Initially, we will only test the route

31:09.530 --> 31:10.860
and not move real goods.

31:12.370 --> 31:13.900
Do we need to be so cautious?

31:20.370 --> 31:22.020
We can't let the higher-ups know

31:22.020 --> 31:23.370
we're stashing anything,

31:23.370 --> 31:24.450
and we definitely can't let them know

31:24.450 --> 31:26.110
we're moving goods on our own.

31:26.310 --> 31:27.240
Don't you agree,

31:27.970 --> 31:28.650
Boss Li?

31:42.410 --> 31:43.170
Boss He,

31:43.540 --> 31:45.270
I've been thinking these days.

31:46.410 --> 31:47.130
About what?

31:48.300 --> 31:51.300
I'm worried Cheng
might try to step over you to rise up.

31:56.650 --> 31:58.410
Let's wait until he's done.

31:59.130 --> 32:01.130
Why are you in such a hurry this time?

32:02.940 --> 32:03.630
There might be a big shipment

32:03.630 --> 32:05.200
coming in recently.

32:05.780 --> 32:07.840
It'd be best if it could go through me.

32:14.670 --> 32:16.670
According to Zhao Xiaoyu's friend,

32:16.960 --> 32:19.480
she said that day Zhao Xiaoyu wanted to
go out for some fresh air

32:19.480 --> 32:21.100
and never returned to the bar.

32:21.100 --> 32:22.410
Later, when she texted her,

32:22.410 --> 32:23.860
Xiaoyu said she was a bit tired

32:23.860 --> 32:24.690
and went home.

32:25.590 --> 32:27.320
She went home with this person.

32:27.720 --> 32:29.580
Do we have a clear shot of his face?

32:30.770 --> 32:31.900
That's the problem.

32:32.380 --> 32:35.240
He seemed to be deliberately
avoiding the cameras.

32:35.300 --> 32:36.270
After coming out of the bar,

32:36.270 --> 32:37.990
he took Zhao Xiaoyu into the car.

32:37.990 --> 32:39.190
We didn't catch his face at all.

32:39.190 --> 32:40.850
And the license plate is fake.

32:42.300 --> 32:44.820
Did you check the cameras
near Zhao Xiaoyu's home?

32:44.820 --> 32:47.120
Lishui Residential Area
is an old residential area.

32:47.120 --> 32:49.060
There aren't many cameras to check.

32:49.060 --> 32:50.080
I checked them all,

32:50.080 --> 32:51.140
but found nothing.

32:51.450 --> 32:52.580
Play it for me again.

32:52.900 --> 32:53.250
Okay.

32:57.020 --> 32:59.680
You watch it first.
I need to make some medicine.

33:16.770 --> 33:18.030
Did you find anything?

33:19.410 --> 33:21.210
Can we track this license plate?

33:21.650 --> 33:22.020
Yes.

33:22.100 --> 33:23.160
That's easy. Here.

33:27.610 --> 33:30.740
Bin D2A523.

33:30.740 --> 33:31.170
Is that it?

33:31.170 --> 33:32.590
Bin D2A

33:32.930 --> 33:34.020
523.

33:35.540 --> 33:37.170
Zhao Ping, check this license plate

33:37.170 --> 33:39.430
and see if we can get the dashcam footage.

34:02.410 --> 34:03.610
You two, come with me.

34:07.210 --> 34:09.170
Xiaoyu,

34:10.010 --> 34:13.260
what exactly happened?

34:13.260 --> 34:15.300
My poor Xiaoyu.

34:15.929 --> 34:16.969
Who did this?

34:16.969 --> 34:18.489
Who did this?

34:18.489 --> 34:19.699
Xiaoyu!

34:27.179 --> 34:28.340
Xiaoyu!

34:31.340 --> 34:33.179
Look at Mom.

34:33.969 --> 34:35.860
Why did you turn out like this?

34:44.739 --> 34:45.409
I'm fine.

34:48.370 --> 34:49.900
Why don't you go back first?

34:50.659 --> 34:52.120
It's not good for the baby.

34:53.530 --> 34:54.489
We're fine.

35:01.930 --> 35:03.300
Xiaoyu!

35:06.700 --> 35:09.010
Why did you turn out like this?

35:10.930 --> 35:13.790
It's just like what happened to
my family back then.

35:17.310 --> 35:19.200
My parents were also

35:20.300 --> 35:21.380
crying inside.

35:26.530 --> 35:27.620
I was right here,

35:29.450 --> 35:30.580
in this exact place.

35:33.530 --> 35:35.090
I didn't even dare to go in

35:38.410 --> 35:39.810
and I didn't dare to look.

35:52.140 --> 35:53.220
Chuan,

35:53.940 --> 35:55.190
it's Mom.

35:56.090 --> 35:58.660
Open your eyes and look at me.

35:58.730 --> 36:05.810
[2012]

36:00.970 --> 36:01.530
Qiuyun.

36:02.320 --> 36:02.850
Qiuyun.

36:03.740 --> 36:06.090
How will we live without you?

36:17.780 --> 36:18.700
Jin.

37:25.620 --> 37:27.220
Once it's wrapped up inside,

37:27.890 --> 37:30.140
I'll talk to the victim's parents
about her situation.

37:30.140 --> 37:31.340
Don't worry about it.

37:34.580 --> 37:35.180
By the way,

37:35.700 --> 37:36.560
this afternoon

37:36.930 --> 37:39.370
the criminal investigation teams
from Ningyuan and Xin'gang

37:39.370 --> 37:40.260
are coming over.

37:40.260 --> 37:41.320
There's a lot to do,

37:41.660 --> 37:42.610
and I can't handle it all.

37:42.610 --> 37:43.470
Please help me.

37:48.900 --> 37:50.230
Xiaoyu!

37:50.570 --> 37:52.930
Why did you turn out like this?

37:52.930 --> 37:54.490
Who exactly did this?

37:58.530 --> 37:59.490
Dan,

38:03.420 --> 38:04.420
thank you.

38:35.220 --> 38:35.990
Mr. Wang,

38:36.010 --> 38:38.340
please help us out
and give us some advice.

38:39.970 --> 38:41.770
The great detective is here too?

38:44.050 --> 38:44.980
Long time no see.

38:46.050 --> 38:46.780
Mr. Liu.

38:46.860 --> 38:47.410
Hello.

38:47.430 --> 38:48.780
Leader, do you know each other?

38:48.780 --> 38:49.260
Yes.

38:49.260 --> 38:50.700
When I was first transferred to
the headquarters,

38:50.700 --> 38:52.010
we met a few times.

38:52.590 --> 38:55.320
Now I just hear stories.

38:53.020 --> 38:55.380
[Deputy Captain Liu Zishan, CID,
Binjiang Provincial Public Security Bureau]

38:56.450 --> 38:58.340
These are Captain Fang from Ninghai
and Captain Yu from Xingang.

38:58.340 --> 38:59.700
Hello, Professor Jiang.

38:59.700 --> 39:00.180
Hello.

39:00.490 --> 39:01.260
I've heard so much about you.

39:01.260 --> 39:02.520
I've read your papers.

39:03.070 --> 39:03.760
Leaders,

39:03.780 --> 39:04.450
let's go inside to talk.

39:04.450 --> 39:04.930
Okay.

39:15.180 --> 39:16.050
You're pretty impressive.

39:16.050 --> 39:17.050
Professor Jiang.

39:17.530 --> 39:18.010
Come on.

39:18.220 --> 39:19.280
Please take a seat.

39:25.370 --> 39:26.140
In the past,

39:26.170 --> 39:27.780
I used to hear Mr. Wang
talk about you all the time.

39:27.780 --> 39:29.530
I've read

39:29.550 --> 39:31.260
your research notes and case analyses.

39:31.260 --> 39:33.620
I didn't expect we'd get a chance
to work together.

39:33.620 --> 39:35.150
You're a real young talent.

39:35.690 --> 39:36.440
Thank you.

39:37.530 --> 39:39.060
How does it feel teaching

39:39.090 --> 39:40.570
at the Haizhou University
of Political Science and Law?

39:40.570 --> 39:42.300
Everything is going smoothly.

39:42.780 --> 39:43.890
You're leaving the front line.

39:43.890 --> 39:45.420
With all your great skills,

39:45.740 --> 39:48.010
it really feels like
you're being underutilized.

39:48.010 --> 39:49.140
I wouldn't say I'm underutilized.

39:49.140 --> 39:50.270
It's a very good job.

39:51.570 --> 39:52.180
Mr. Wang,

39:52.780 --> 39:55.220
A great teacher
produces a brilliant student.

39:55.220 --> 39:58.350
The brilliant student
will soon become a great teacher.

40:01.450 --> 40:02.820
Mr. Liu, let's begin.

40:03.010 --> 40:03.570
Okay.

40:04.660 --> 40:05.220
Zhou Jin!

40:05.740 --> 40:06.470
Let's begin.

40:14.310 --> 40:15.060
Leaders,

40:15.180 --> 40:15.980
and comrades,

40:16.060 --> 40:17.660
the materials for the 3 cases

40:17.690 --> 40:18.860
have been prepared

40:18.880 --> 40:20.030
and are at your disposal.

40:20.030 --> 40:21.840
I'll now give you an update

40:21.860 --> 40:23.280
on the latest progress
in the Zhao Xiaoyu case

40:23.280 --> 40:24.240
in Haizhou City.

40:27.960 --> 40:29.270
The deceased is Zhao Xiaoyu,

40:29.270 --> 40:30.580
female, 27 years old.

40:29.740 --> 40:32.710
[Zhao Xiaoyu Case in
Lishui Residential Area]

40:30.860 --> 40:33.220
On August 23, 2017,

40:33.220 --> 40:34.740
at 10:46 a.m.,

40:34.740 --> 40:35.940
we received a report.

40:36.090 --> 40:38.180
The victim died in her own home.

40:38.870 --> 40:39.610
The scene is located in

40:39.610 --> 40:42.670
Nancheng District,
Haizhou City, Binjiang Province.

41:06.850 --> 41:08.260
Let's first take a look
at the crime scene.

41:08.260 --> 41:10.060
Pay close attention to this car.

41:10.140 --> 41:11.490
Based on its position,

41:11.730 --> 41:13.210
if the dashcam

41:13.230 --> 41:14.490
was working properly,

41:14.620 --> 41:15.820
there's a high chance

41:15.820 --> 41:18.420
it captured a clear view
of the suspect's face.

41:19.140 --> 41:19.890
Don't worry.

41:19.890 --> 41:21.690
Once our Investigator Zhao Ping returns,

41:21.690 --> 41:23.150
everything will be clear.

41:24.490 --> 41:25.570
Okay, next let's take a look

41:25.570 --> 41:26.810
at the photos of the crime scene.

41:26.810 --> 41:29.040
[Zhao Xiaoyu Case in
Lishui Residential Area]

41:40.370 --> 41:41.170
Wait a minute.

41:42.700 --> 41:44.360
Go back to the previous frame.

42:04.410 --> 42:06.740
Did you find something, Professor Jiang?

42:44.640 --> 42:45.990
What are you looking at?

42:52.130 --> 42:54.340
Is there something wrong with my skirt?

43:07.490 --> 43:09.120
The criminal wasn't satisfied
with their skirts.
